Hello, this game is a strategy game.
There are only few things you have to know:
1) Place the weapons to attack the enemies.
2) Stop the enemies from reaching the end.
3) The enemies and the weapons are shapes.
4) You have three lives.
5) Enemies keep on coming, increasingly.
6) Your goal is to maintain as long as possible.
Lastly, Make sure you place the weapons wisely,
You can only have three.
Good Luck